homepage.heading: Front End Developer
homepage.p1: With over 8 years of versatile experience spanning digital marketing to frontend development, I began my career in performance marketing. Successfully steering growth strategies for property and retail companies, I expertly managed diverse digital advertising channels such as PPC, social advertising, and affiliate marketing.
homepage.p2: In my recent role as a Frontend Engineer, I've deepened my expertise in web technologies. Proficient in HTML, CSS, Javascript, Typescript, React, and Next.js, I bring a comprehensive skill set to the dynamic field of frontend development.
